          <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
          <h2 id="traditional-vs-online-prop-trading">Traditional vs Online Prop Trading</h2>

          <p>Prop trading generally falls into two models: traditional in-house desks and online prop firms. Both use firm capital, but how you're assessed and managed is very different.</p>

          <div class="not-prose grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-4 my-8">
